ygData.messageBody:
There have been hardly any votes on the poll for EQ hacks. I am
beginning to think you people don't care, I might as well just send
an email with the hacks to the only FOUR people who voted. C'mon, I
have checked every day, and NO ONE votes. This group is for these
kinds of things, and well, no one wants them but 4 people. I expect
atleast 30 votes on the poll, or I will just email the hacks for EQ
to the people who want them. All the people who didn't vote then, if
there are less than 30, will not get these and will not have another
chance unless they look for a few hours on the internet finding them.
Sorry people, BUT THERE ARE ONLY 4 VOTES.
